      • addSplitField

        public static org.geotools.feature.simple.SimpleFeatureBuilder addSplitField(org.opengis.feature.simple.SimpleFeatureType schema)
        Create a builder out of a SimpleFeatureCollection's schema and add a mark field of type int. The mark name can be set with the method MarkParcelAttributeFromPosition.setMarkFieldName(String).
        Parameters:
        schema -
        Returns:
        a SimpleFeatureBuilder felative to the schema + a marking field
